{"tid":2401494,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣上車盤急反彈 荃景花園呎價1.59萬歷史新高　","createTime":"2021-02-09T18:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T04:11:47.000Z","uid":388012,"like":8,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f20c51afab9fda186c5dfa40001d970197434c","tid":2401494,"uid":388012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"hket<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荃灣上車盤急反彈 荃景花園呎價1.59萬歷史新高　<br />\n私樓成交<br />\n13:30 2021/02/09<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二手氣氛回旺，上車盤造價回升，荃灣上車盤集中地的荃景圍二手反應理想，當中荃景花園細單位價錢重現600萬元，呎價1.59萬破盡荃景花園歷史紀錄，向1.6萬進發。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業助理區域經理鍾家豪表示，荃景花園2期12座極高層F室，實用面積380平方呎，業主開價610萬元，僅輕微減價5萬元售出，成交價605萬元，呎價15,921元。鍾家豪表現，是次成交單位屬荃景花園細兩房房重上600萬元。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，荃景花園11座高層F室，實用面積380平方呎，2019登記價錢為635萬及呎價1.67萬元，惟該成交屬內部轉讓。因此，是次成12座極高層單位呎價創荃景花園呎價歷史新高紀錄。"},{"pid":"6eaa393287e054a60cd61a5d5ae241aabefce2d4","tid":2401494,"uid":60959,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"樓主AA狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53d461cd516396f841a5c9dd64b3f18d6ed55ae","tid":2401494,"uid":388012,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6eaa393287e054a60cd61a5d5ae241aabefce2d4","tid":2401494,"uid":60959,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"樓主AA狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"我點會做aa 呢D 工作"},{"pid":"0ade920f2618dbc1e8c1a76b450bc8b3b5956eb1","tid":2401494,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"6eaa393287e054a60cd61a5d5ae241aabefce2d4","tid":2401494,"uid":60959,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"樓主AA狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T19:46:37.000Z","msg":"on9當有趣"},{"pid":"5a5d113ba8376a5a464601abaca1d2232eece3dd","tid":2401494,"uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":2,"